====future plans====


You already have addToPlanner wired up in ToDoListItem. The reverse — dragging a to-do item directly onto the day planner grid — would close the loop and feel very natural.

The streak data is already tracked per routine item. A small "personal bests" panel in the routine view showing longest-ever streaks would add gamification without new backend work.

